<div id="fb_body_wrapper">
<div id="fb_tab">
<div id="fb_tab_l">Op&eacute;rateur Shl (D&eacute;calage &agrave; gauche)</div>
<div id="fb_tab_r">&nbsp;<img src="images/fblogo_mini.gif" /></div> 
</div> 
<div id="fb_pg_wrapper">
<div id="fb_pg_body">
	D&eacute;cale vers la gauche les bits d'une expression num&eacute;rique<br \>
<br \>
<div class="fb_sect_title">Syntaxe</div><div class="fb_sect_cont"><tt><br \>
<a href="KeyPgDeclare.html">Declare</a> <a href="KeyPgOperator.html">Operator</a> <b>Shl</b> ( <a href="KeyPgByref.html">ByRef</a> <i>lhs</i> <a href="KeyPgAs.html">As</a> <a href="KeyPgInteger.html">Integer</a>, <a href="KeyPgByref.html">ByRef</a> <i>rhs</i> <a href="KeyPgAs.html">As</a> <a href="KeyPgInteger.html">Integer</a> ) <a href="KeyPgAs.html">As</a> <a href="KeyPgInteger.html">Integer</a><br \>
<a href="KeyPgDeclare.html">Declare</a> <a href="KeyPgOperator.html">Operator</a> <b>Shl</b> ( <a href="KeyPgByref.html">ByRef</a> <i>lhs</i> <a href="KeyPgAs.html">As</a> <a href="KeyPgUinteger.html">UInteger</a>, <a href="KeyPgByref.html">ByRef</a> <i>rhs</i> <a href="KeyPgAs.html">As</a> <a href="KeyPgUinteger.html">UInteger</a> ) <a href="KeyPgAs.html">As</a> <a href="KeyPgUinteger.html">UInteger</a><br \>
<a href="KeyPgDeclare.html">Declare</a> <a href="KeyPgOperator.html">Operator</a> <b>Shl</b> ( <a href="KeyPgByref.html">ByRef</a> <i>lhs</i> <a href="KeyPgAs.html">As</a> <a href="KeyPgLongint.html">LongInt</a>, <a href="KeyPgByref.html">ByRef</a> <i>rhs</i> <a href="KeyPgAs.html">As</a> <a href="KeyPgLongint.html">LongInt</a> ) <a href="KeyPgAs.html">As</a> <a href="KeyPgLongint.html">LongInt</a><br \>
<a href="KeyPgDeclare.html">Declare</a> <a href="KeyPgOperator.html">Operator</a> <b>Shl</b> ( <a href="KeyPgByref.html">ByRef</a> <i>lhs</i> <a href="KeyPgAs.html">As</a> <a href="KeyPgUlongint.html">ULongInt</a>, <a href="KeyPgByref.html">ByRef</a> <i>rhs</i> <a href="KeyPgAs.html">As</a> <a href="KeyPgUlongint.html">ULongInt</a> ) <a href="KeyPgAs.html">As</a> <a href="KeyPgUlongint.html">ULongInt</a><br \>
</tt><br \>
</div><div class="fb_sect_title">Usage</div><div class="fb_sect_cont"><tt><br \>
<i>result</i> = <i>lhs</i> <b>Shl</b> <i>rhs</i><br \>
</tt><br \>
</div><div class="fb_sect_title">Param&egrave;tres</div><div class="fb_sect_cont"><br \>
<tt><i>lhs</i></tt><br \>
<div class="fb_indent">La valeur de l'op&eacute;ration de d&eacute;calage.<br \>
</div><tt><i>rhs</i></tt><br \>
<div class="fb_indent">Le nombre de bits de d&eacute;calage.<br \>
<br \>
</div></div><div class="fb_sect_title">Valeur retourn&eacute;e</div><div class="fb_sect_cont"><br \>
Retourne le r&eacute;sultat du d&eacute;calage de <tt><i>rhs</i></tt> bits vers la gauche de la valeur <tt><i>lhs</i></tt>.<br \>
<br \>
</div><div class="fb_sect_title">Description</div><div class="fb_sect_cont"><br \>
L'<b><tt>Op&eacute;rateur Shl</tt> (D&eacute;calage vers la gauche)</b> d&eacute;cale vers la gauche tous les bits de l'expression de gauche (<tt><i>lhs</i></tt>) un nombre de fois sp&eacute;cifi&eacute; dans l'expression de droite (<tt><i>rhs</i></tt>). Cela a pour effet de multiplier <tt><i>lhs</i></tt> par deux pour chaque d&eacute;calage. Par exemple, "<tt>&b0101 <b>Shl</b> 1</tt>" retourne le nombre binaire <tt>&b01010</tt>, et "<tt>5 <b>Shl</b> 1</tt>" retourne <tt>10</tt>.<br \>
<br \>
Dans tous les cas, aucun op&eacute;rande n'est modifi&eacute;.<br \>
<br \>
Cet op&eacute;rateur peut &ecirc;tre surcharg&eacute; pour accepter les types d&eacute;finis par l'utilisateur.<br \>
<br \>
</div><div class="fb_sect_title">Exemple</div><div class="fb_sect_cont"><br \>
<tt><div class="freebasic">
<span class="com">'Double&nbsp;a&nbsp;number</span><br />
<span class="key">For</span>&nbsp;<span class="wrd">i</span>&nbsp;<span class="key">As</span>&nbsp;<span class="key">Integer</span>&nbsp;<span class="oth">=</span>&nbsp;<span class="num">0</span>&nbsp;<span class="key">To</span>&nbsp;<span class="num">10</span><br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="key">Print</span>&nbsp;<span class="num">5</span>&nbsp;<span class="key">Shl</span>&nbsp;<span class="wrd">i</span><span class="oth">,</span>&nbsp;<span class="key">Bin</span><span class="oth">(</span><span class="num">5</span>&nbsp;<span class="key">Shl</span>&nbsp;<span class="wrd">i</span><span class="oth">,</span>&nbsp;<span class="num">16</span><span class="oth">)</span><br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />
<span class="key">Next</span>&nbsp;<span class="wrd">i</span><br />
</div></tt><br />
Affiche:<br \>
<pre class="fb_pre">
 5            0000000000000101
 10           0000000000001010
 20           0000000000010100
 40           0000000000101000
 80           0000000001010000
 160          0000000010100000
 320          0000000101000000
 640          0000001010000000
 1280         0000010100000000
 2560         0000101000000000
 5120         0001010000000000
</pre><br \>
<br \>
</div><div class="fb_sect_title">Diff&eacute;rences de dialecte</div><div class="fb_sect_cont"><br \>
<ul><li> Non disponible dans le dialecte <i><a href="CompilerOptlang.html">-lang qb</a></i> sauf si r&eacute;f&eacute;renc&eacute; avec l'alias <tt><b>__Shl</b></tt>.<br \>
<br \>
</ul></div><div class="fb_sect_title">Diff&eacute;rences avec QB</div><div class="fb_sect_cont"><br \>
<ul><li> Nouveau pour FreeBASIC<br \>
<br \>
